title: Jesse Barnett from Stick To Your Guns
itunes:title: Jesse Barnett from Stick To Your Guns
description:
Episode 5 - One fine Southern California afternoon, Jesse Barnett (the vocalist from Stick To Your Guns) and I spoke candidly about relationships, why they've never been "accepted" by the hardcore scene and religion. It's one of my favorite conversations I have had on the show thus far.
